<doc id="1228253" wikidata="Q173693" url="?curid=1228253" title="Bruce Johnstone (racing driver)">
<text>William Bruce Gordon Johnstone (30 January 1937 – 3 March 2022) was a South African racing driver. He participated in one Formula One (F1) World Championship Grand Prix, on 29 December 1962. He scored no championship points. He also competed in the F1 non-championship 1962 Oulton Park Gold Cup where he finished fourth and in the South African Formula 1 Championship.

Johnstone died on 3 March 2022, at the age of 85.

