<doc id="1228306" wikidata="Q172990" url="?curid=1228306" title="Domenico Schiattarella">
<text>Domenico &quot;Mimmo&quot; Schiattarella (born 17 November 1967) is an Italian racing driver. He participated in 7 Formula One Grands Prix for Simtek, debuting on October 16, 1994, and finishing when the team folded the next year. He scored no championship points, with a best finish of 9th in the 1995 Argentine Grand Prix. He has also participated in several CART races, Le Mans Series and American Le Mans Series events.

