<doc id="1228338" wikidata="Q61459" url="?curid=1228338" title="Ernst Klodwig">
<text>Ernst Klodwig (23 May 1903 – 15 April 1973) was an East German racing driver. He participated in two Formula One World Championship Grands Prix, driving privately run BMWs with different engines. He was classified in both races with a best finish of 12th.
